newsitem.title: MALAYSIA: Malaysia Dec palm oil exports 702,082 tonnes-Caleb.
newsitem.headline: Malaysia Dec palm oil exports 702,082 tonnes-Caleb.

text.p: Cargo surveyor Caleb Brett put Malaysia's December bulk palm oil exports at 702,082 tonnes against its estimate of 673,905 for November, traders said.
The figures include laurics and oleochemicals but exclude shipments to Singapore and exports in drum, said the traders who obtained the data by facsimile.
The official Palm Oil Registration and Licensing Authority put November exports at 632,441 tonnes.
